text:
Slow slow service. 7 customers on queue but only one CSO attending to these customers although there are 2 other staff standing behind the counter.
No privacy when you discuss with CSO about funds placement or funds withdrawal.
CSO is polite, pleasant

While scouting for better FD interest rates, I chanced upon this branch at Towner Road. The branch is neat and clean. The staff Miss Wendy has been very polite and helpful in explaining the products and process our application very efficiently. It has been a good banking experience.
Staff not friendly n flexible enough in handing issue. Other Singapura finance branches can do it, why not here?
Staffs Wendy and Felicia are both very patient to explain and respect what we want to do in our savings and FD.
